Alert!!!!

Don't sign ANY paper work until you have FULLY inspected the bus and are 
sure there was no addition damage.  Fine print on the paper work says "any 
claims must be made with driver present and must be signed by driver".

I could have claimed my battery damage if I would have caught it.
